1
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:33,799
So it's Xu Xuejiao.

2
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,159
She seems to be

3
00:01:35,159 --> 00:01:36,799
Haicheng's Genius Female Doctor, right?

4
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,640
This figure...

5
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:39,840
is really hot.

6
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:45,239
Where are you looking?

7
00:01:46,079 --> 00:01:46,359
Ah!

8
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,200
I...

9
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,159
Hey!

10
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:51,400
I...

11
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:53,799
Ah!

12
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:59,000
Why is her temper even hotter than her figure?

13
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:01,799
Being so violent,

14
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:03,959
does it do justice to her looks?

15
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,280
What did you say?

16
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,680
I didn't say anything.

17
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,159
His lips really didn't move just now.

18
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,199
Could it be that I heard his inner thoughts?

19
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:15,560
She should also be one of Gu Zhantian's spare tires.

20
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,759
I'd better make our relationship

21
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:17,639
a bit more strained first,

22
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:19,000
so we interact less in the future.

23
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,479
Oh.

24
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,280
As expected,

25
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,280
I can do mind-reading by looking into his eyes.

26
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,360
How fun.

27
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:25,960
Xuejiao,

28
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,960
I'm done saying hello.

29
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:29,680
I'll be leaving now.

30
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:34,199
Don't be in such a hurry to leave,

31
00:02:34,199 --> 00:02:34,960
Young Master Lu.

32
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,800
In the past,

33
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,879
didn't you love pestering me the most,

34
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:42,199
asking all sorts of questions,

35
00:02:42,199 --> 00:02:44,159
and even wanting to see me in a nurse's uniform?

36
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,639
What's wrong?

37
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:46,879
Have you changed your ways?

38
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:49,680
Mmm.

39
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:58,960
This figure...

40
00:02:58,960 --> 00:02:59,759
This voice...

41
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:00,879
No way.

42
00:03:00,879 --> 00:03:01,879
I must hold on.

43
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,199
I...

44
00:03:04,199 --> 00:03:05,680
was just blind before.

45
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:07,680
I have no interest in you now.

46
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,479
Oh?

47
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,759
No interest?

48
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,879
Then just now,

49
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:16,120
whose eyes

50
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:18,000
almost fell into my cleavage?

51
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,800
Men who lie

52
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,080
have to swallow silver needles.

53
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,599
No.

54
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,639
If she keeps pestering me, there's going to be trouble.

55
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:46,879
Calm down.

56
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,159
Fight back.

57
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:58,439
Sis Xuejiao,

58
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,960
you care so much about where I look,

59
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,680
could it be that you're enjoying it?

60
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:14,280
Ah!

61
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:17,959
He...

62
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:18,879
How dare he!

63
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,600
Unfortunately,

64
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,160
I'm busy today.

65
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:26,079
As for your figure...

66
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,600
I've seen enough of it,

67
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,480
and it's just so-so.

68
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:31,439
Lu Chengwen!

69
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,560
You jerk!

70
00:04:32,759 --> 00:04:34,040
Let go of me!

71
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,399
Sis Xuejiao,

72
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,439
