73
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,439
You're still too green.

74
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,160
Go on.

75
00:04:48,439 --> 00:04:49,800
Go to Old Master Chen

76
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,800
and treat his illness.

77
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,399
Little girl.

78
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,079
Ah!

79
00:04:57,879 --> 00:05:00,160
He actually called me a little girl!

80
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:01,639
And he dared to push me!

81
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:03,040
Go to hell!

82
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,839
However...

83
00:05:04,839 --> 00:05:06,639
he used to be so disgusting and creepy.

84
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:08,839
Why is he acting so manly today?

85
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,639
He made my heart beat so fast.

86
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:11,839
That jerk!

87
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:13,759
You...

88
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,399
Just you wait!

89
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,160
That was a close call.

90
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,160
This girl is on another level.

91
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,959
I couldn't have handled her without playing hardball.

92
00:05:28,399 --> 00:05:30,000
Good thing I've read a lot of power fantasy novels.

93
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,000
It actually worked.

94
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,360
But...

95
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,399
Where did this quack doctor come from?

96
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:36,399
Daring to call himself a Miracle Doctor?

97
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,759
You can't discuss ice with a summer insect.

98
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,480
What's all this about ice?

99
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,839
I think you're the one who's seriously sick.

100
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,800
Get lost!

101
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,639
Isn't that Gu Zhantian's voice?

102
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,000
I can't let him see me.

103
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:49,160
I better run.

104
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:52,759
Wait.

105
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:53,560
That's not right.

106
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:55,399
I've seen this kind of plot before!

107
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,879
It must be that Xu Xuejiao's medical skills aren't

108
00:05:56,879 --> 00:05:57,480
proficient enough,

109
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,959
and she almost kills Old Master Chen.

110
00:05:59,759 --> 00:06:01,160
Then Gu Zhantian steps in to help,

111
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,680
and wins her over.

112
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,160
Stop loitering around here.

113
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,000
Hurry up and leave.

114
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,879
If I run away now,

115
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:10,680
then Old Master Chen is definitely dead!

116
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:12,160
What should I do?

117
00:06:21,079 --> 00:06:22,199
As long as you nod,

118
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,199
I can make this person

119
00:06:23,199 --> 00:06:24,480
disappear forever.

120
00:06:26,879 --> 00:06:27,360
Oh, well.

121
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,600
It's a human life, after all.

122
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:29,480
Besides,

123
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,000
I'll do Gu Zhantian a favor.

124
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,959
It might ease his hatred for me a bit.

125
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,560
If you don't leave, I'll call the police!

126
00:06:37,279 --> 00:06:38,079
Butler!

127
00:06:38,759 --> 00:06:39,560
Lu Chengwen.

128
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:41,040
Why is it you again?

129
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:43,560
How dare you call Young Master Lu by his name!

130
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,399
Get lost!

131
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,160
The butler is courting death!

132
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,240
Don't drag me down with you!

133
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,000
Don't be rude.

134
00:06:50,759 --> 00:06:51,839
This is my friend.

135
00:06:53,199 --> 00:06:54,279
Ah.

136
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,160
My apologies.

137
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:55,759
My apologies.

138
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,839
Mr. Gu.

139
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:57,560
Young Master Lu.

140
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,000
But today, neither of you

141
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,000
can see Old Master Chen.

142
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,759
This idiot.

143
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,000
If we don't see him today,

144
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,439
we'll never have to see him again.

145
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:06,639
Ah.

146
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:07,439
Well,

147
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,560
I just thought about it,

148
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:11,399
and I feel like I did something wrong.

149
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,639
I originally planned

150
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:13,879
to return these billions

151
00:07:13,879 --> 00:07:15,399
to Old Master Chen.

152
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,480
But with your attitude,

153
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,560
I won't return it.

154
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:19,279
To get me through the door,

155
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,839
he's willing to spend so much money.

156
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:22,000
Young Master Lu,

157
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,120
what you're saying...

158
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,160
How am I supposed to respond?

159
00:07:24,519 --> 00:07:25,319
Ah.

160
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:26,560
Hard to respond, right?

161
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:27,560
That's fine.

162
00:07:27,759 --> 00:07:29,560
I'll go back and have someone tell Old Master Chen

163
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,800
that I wanted to return billions to him,

164
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,399
but you kicked me out.

165
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:32,879
Hey!

166
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:33,800
No, no, no, no, no!

167
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:34,759
Well,

168
00:07:34,759 --> 00:07:35,399
you two

169
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,439
should just go in.

170
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:38,040
Just pretend I don't exist.

171
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:38,800
I don't exist.

172
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,560
Haha.

173
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,560
Let's go in.

174
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:53,160
Gu Zhantian.

175
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:57,160
Xuejiao.

176
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,199
Long time no see.

177
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,120
Hmm.

178
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,399
What's going on?

179
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:05,920
I feel like I'm sensing some

180
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,160
weird character dynamics.

181
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:11,000
Our engagement was arranged by our ancestors.

182
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,839
It wasn't my intention.

183
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,800
I hope you'll stop pestering me.

184
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,240
Okay.

185
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:17,040
Here comes the familiar trope.

186
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,279
I'm only here for the treatment today.

187
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,240
Hah.

188
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,839
I heard you used to be a security guard.

189
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:24,000
Now even gatekeepers

190
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,160
can treat illnesses?

191
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,160
Gu Zhantian,

192
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,040
I'm doing the treatment right now.

193
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,080
It's not your place to interfere.

194
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,759
Keep arguing.

195
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:38,559
This little girl is just too noisy.

196
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,159
Let's see you get slapped in the face later.

197
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:42,840
Lu Chengwen,

198
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,039
what are you doing here?

199
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:44,519
Ah.

200
00:08:45,159 --> 00:08:46,279
I, uh...

201
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:47,759
Brother Zhantian and I are

202
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,399
friends.

203
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:49,360
I

204
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,080
came with him.

205
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:50,879
You guys continue.

206
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,759
Th-th-this...

207
00:08:58,759 --> 00:08:59,159
What?

208
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:05,320
Ah!

209
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,120
Ah!

210
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:14,399
This is the effect of King Wen's Medical Tome!

211
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,360
The acupoints are completely visible!

212
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,399
So amazing!

213
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:18,120
Lu Chengwen

214
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:18,639
has actually read

215
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:19,600
King Wen's Medical Tome!

216
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,840
That mass of dark qi near the heart meridian

217
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,399
must be the root of the illness.

218
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:41,120
This little witch

219
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,399
really did needle the wrong spot.

220
00:09:42,399 --> 00:09:43,399
Gu Zhantian,

221
00:09:43,399 --> 00:09:44,440
I'm counting on you.

222
00:09:45,039 --> 00:09:45,799
Dark qi?

223
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:46,840
The root is in the heart meridian?

224
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:48,120
Could it be...

225
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,559
he possesses King Wen's Vision?

226
00:09:49,799 --> 00:09:50,679
That was close.

227
00:09:51,159 --> 00:09:52,279
I almost needled the wrong spot

228
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:53,279
and killed Grandpa Chen.

229
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,200
Xuejiao,

230
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,399
let me do it.

231
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:57,759
Don't delay the treatment.

232
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:58,639
Quiet!

233
00:09:58,639 --> 00:09:59,879
You have no right to speak here.

234
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:01,600
Your medical skills are not yet refined.

235
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,000
Don't be impulsive.

236
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:23,200
*Cough, cough, cough*

237
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:27,000
She actually got it right.

238
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:30,159
Hmph.

239
00:10:31,879 --> 00:10:32,679
Xuejiao,

240
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,200
you adapted to the situation

241
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,279
and changed the needle path in time.

242
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:36,080
Although

243
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,360
your technique was a bit rough,

244
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:38,240
and the force

245
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,200
and control were lacking,

246
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,360
failing to use one needle

247
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,240
to eradicate the root of the illness,

248
00:10:41,559 --> 00:10:42,960
but

249
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:43,799
it still managed to avoid

250
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,960
the worst outcome.

251
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,159
No,

252
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,000
bro,

253
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,799
if you can't speak nicely, then shut up.

254
00:10:48,799 --> 00:10:50,080
Who wants to hear that?

255
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,080
Rough technique?

256
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:53,360
Lacking control?

257
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:54,799
Are your eyes on top of your head?

258
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:55,639
Just now,

259
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:56,679
if it weren't for me...

260
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:57,480
I...

261
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:59,480
If I hadn't heard a certain jerk's inner voice,

262
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,360
Grandpa Chen would be gone.

263
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,480
Besides standing here

264
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,440
making snide remarks,

265
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,240
what else can you do?

266
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,360
Let me tell you,

267
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,159
our engagement,

268
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,559
from this moment on,

269
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:08,279
is completely,

270
00:11:08,279 --> 00:11:09,000
forever,

271
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:09,919
and entirely void!

272
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,639
Disappear from my sight immediately!

273
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,240
Darn it.

274
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:17,440
Will I get caught in the crossfire later?

275
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:18,559
I better slip away.

276
00:11:19,799 --> 00:11:20,039
Hey,

277
00:11:20,039 --> 00:11:20,840
um,

278
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,039
Brother Zhantian,

279
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:22,559
I

280
00:11:22,559 --> 00:11:23,440
just remembered

281
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:23,960
I have something to do.

282
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,799
I'll get going.

283
00:11:24,799 --> 00:11:25,120
You guys

284
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:25,600
carry on.

285
00:11:25,799 --> 00:11:26,600
Lu Chengwen,

286
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:28,080
you stay.
